title: Increase Height and Enhance Style With JS FOOTWEAR - Designed by InventHelp Client (DHM-112)
text:
A leading invention submission company, InventHelp is submitting J'S FOOTWEAR to companies for their consideration.
PITTSBURGH, PA (PRWEB) October 20, 2015
"My wife always complains about foot pain caused by wearing high heels all day, and many people want to personalize their shoes, especially if they play sports," said an inventor from Knightdale, N.C. "This inspired me to pursue my idea."
J'S FOOTWEAR provides a convenient, comfortable way to increase one’s height. It eliminates the need to wear high heels. It also enhances the user’s style. Though it's beneficial to the general population it's ideal for women, athletes and children.
The original design was submitted to the Durham office of InventHelp. It is currently available for licensing or sale to manufacturers or marketers. For more information, write Dept. 14-DHM-112, InventHelp, 217 Ninth Street, Pittsburgh, PA 15222, or call (412) 288-1300 ext. 1368. Learn more about InventHelp's Invention Submission Services at http://www.InventHelp.com - https://www.youtube.com/user/inventhelp
